Cluff Gold Awarded Exploration License in ‘Highly Prospective’ Mali Area

-- B y   A m a n d a   J o r d a n
-- 
2011-04-04T06:05:09Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-04/cluff-gold-awarded-exploration-license-in-highly-prospective-mali-area.html
Cluff Gold Plc (CLF)  was awarded a gold
exploration license in western  Mali . The permit area is located
300 kilometers west of Bamako in the “highly prospective” Mali
Birrimian Kenieba Inlier Belt, the company said in a statement.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Amanda Jordan in London at 
